snippet.title: The Sims 4 Vintage Glamour Stuff: Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Indulge your Sims in the glamorous life and treat them to an elegant new look with The Sims 4 Vintage Glamour Stuff.

Learn more about this Stuff Pack: http://x.ea.com/26375  

Dress Sims in stunning vintage fashion and accessories then try on makeup at the vanity table. Decorate with high-end furnishings, even hire a butler to fulfill your Sim’s every need.

Don’t miss a trailer for The Sims 4: http://bit.ly/2gmMGUj
